mexico veg oil tax not aim at sunflow -- usda the mexican secretariat of commerc ha told the u.s. that recent implement of a 10 pct ad valorem tariff for fix veget oil , fluid or solid , crude , refin or purifi , wa not target at sunflow oil , the u.s. agricultur depart said . in it world product and trade report , the depart said the increas in tariff on thi categori which includ sunflow , corn and rapese oil , wa a reaction to import use basket categori to avoid pay tariff on specif high-tariff product .